it was cocaine

29:50.917 --> 29:52.458
in the glove compartment.

29:52.458 --> 29:54.625
I thought it was powdered sugar,
you know?

29:54.625 --> 29:56.041
I was trying to make,
like, uh, you know,

29:56.041 --> 29:57.667
- a funnel cake.
- [man] Yeah.

29:57.667 --> 29:59.000
[Daryll] Well,
why would you think

29:59.000 --> 30:00.291
sugar was in the glove
compartment?

30:00.291 --> 30:02.125
[Bunchy] I-I don't know.

30:02.125 --> 30:04.250
- [voices fade]
- [faint hoofbeats]

30:04.250 --> 30:05.333
[Mickey]
It's not funny.

30:05.333 --> 30:09.250
[hoofbeats]

30:15.792 --> 30:18.792
♪ dramatic music ♪

30:18.792 --> 30:22.959
♪♪♪

30:28.417 --> 30:32.333
[hyperventilating]

30:39.333 --> 30:42.458
[retching]

