Oh, my God.

31:11.000 --> 31:13.375
Mom? Mom? Mom?

31:13.375 --> 31:14.875
Oh, okay, h-hold on.

31:14.875 --> 31:18.208
Let me call an ambulance
for you, okay?

31:18.208 --> 31:20.667
Hey...hey, I'm calling
an ambulance.

31:20.667 --> 31:22.417
- Hold on.
- No.

31:22.417 --> 31:23.750
- It's okay. Just one second.
- No, Bridge.

31:23.750 --> 31:25.709
No, Mom, no,
you need a doctor.

31:25.709 --> 31:27.500
- No more doctors.
- No, you need a doctor, Mom.

31:27.500 --> 31:30.041
- No more doctors.
- Mom, you need a doctor.

31:30.041 --> 31:32.917
- No more doctors.
- Okay, okay.

31:32.917 --> 31:36.709
Hey, what--okay, what--
what can I do?

31:36.709 --> 31:38.041
Just get me outside.

31:38.041 --> 31:39.625
- Outside? Okay.
- Outside.

31:39.625 --> 31:41.375
- Okay, hold on.
- Yes, baby.

31:41.375 --> 31:43.041
Okay, I'll take you outside.
Okay, here you go, Mommy.

31:43.041 --> 31:45.041
- Get me outside.
- It's okay. It's okay.

31:45.041 --> 31:48.542
It's okay.
You need a doctor, Mom.

31:48.542 --> 31:51.000
Okay, here, I'll help you.
Here, come here. Come here.

31:51.000 --> 31:54.375
Come here.
Here, get your feet up, okay?

31:54.375 --> 31:56.542
Ready? One, two, three.

31:56.542 --> 31:59.417
[panting]

31:59.417 --> 32:00.583
You're good.
You're standing. You okay?

32:00.583 --> 32:03.417
[sighs]

32:03.417 --> 32:05.417
Just take a second.
You're fine.

32:07.000 --> 32:10.417
All right. Just get some air.
[clears throat]

32:10.417 --> 32:12.500
Okay, okay.

32:13.500 --> 32:18.083
Okay. It's okay.

32:18.083 --> 32:20.250
[indistinct chatter]

32:24.166 --> 32:25.583
[speaking inaudibly]

32:25.583 --> 32:28.625
I got it.

32:28.625 --> 32:30.667
Hey, sweetheart.

32:30.667 --> 32:33.291
Let's go. Come on.

32:33.291 --> 32:34.542
All right, all right.

32:34.542 --> 32:37.041
Take your mom.

32:49.291 --> 32:51.166
Oh, he's getting you a chair.

33:00.166 --> 33:01.542
Here, I got it.

33:03.959 --> 33:05.250
Thanks, Terry.

33:06.417 --> 33:07.083
Okay, okay.

33:10.458 --> 33:11.917
I'm all right.

33:14.000 --> 33:15.166
Bridge.

33:16.458 --> 33:20.208
Go inside.

33:20.208 --> 33:22.875
Make apologies for me.

33:22.875 --> 33:25.583
Tell everyone
I'm a little tired.

33:25.583 --> 33:28.041
All right?

33:28.041 --> 33:30.166
Go and be
a hostess for a minute.

33:30.166 --> 33:32.000
Mom, I can't do this.

33:32.000 --> 33:34.500
- Then come home.
- I can't do this. I'm sorry.

33:34.500 --> 33:34.875
- Bridge.
- I--

33:34.875 --> 33:38.041
Look at me.

33:38.041 --> 33:39.625
You can.

33:43.792 --> 33:47.208
You'll remember
what you did for me,

33:47.208 --> 33:48.875
and you'll be proud.

33:53.166 --> 33:53.959
- Okay.
- Good girl.

33:53.959 --> 33:56.750
- I'm sorry. Okay.
- Come on.

34:03.792 --> 34:04.250
[sighs]

34:08.000 --> 34:10.000
You got a cigarette?

34:10.000 --> 34:12.333
That's not fuckin' funny.

34:14.583 --> 34:16.834
It's not a fuckin' joke.

34:16.834 --> 34:18.875
I ain't got
a fuckin' cigarette.

34:18.875 --> 34:21.166
- Yes, you do.
- No.

34:21.166 --> 34:23.375
You don't think
I seen you sneak 'em?

34:27.208 --> 34:28.834
Hand it over.

34:52.750 --> 34:54.291
Oh, fuck, that's good.

35:00.083 --> 35:02.208
[coughing]

35:08.208 --> 35:12.542
I'm gonna go
to fuckin' hell for this.

35:12.542 --> 35:13.959
No.

35:15.709 --> 35:17.875
Saint Peter's gonna
give you a hand job

35:17.875 --> 35:19.959
