has been turned off.

35:36.166 --> 35:37.583
Thank you.

35:37.583 --> 35:40.625
♪ tense music ♪

35:40.625 --> 35:45.500
♪♪♪

36:12.458 --> 36:15.333
[rumbling]

36:23.000 --> 36:26.458
- All right?
- Yeah.

36:38.333 --> 36:40.959
- All right?
- Yeah.

36:43.667 --> 36:46.125
Comfortable?

36:48.041 --> 36:50.166
- All right.
- Oh, thanks, Terry.

36:51.000 --> 36:53.000
I'll get the blanket.

37:06.000 --> 37:07.333
- Good?
- Yeah.

37:12.500 --> 37:15.333
Honey...

37:15.333 --> 37:18.208
I'm just gonna sleep
for a couple hours.

37:18.208 --> 37:19.375
All right.

37:19.375 --> 37:21.917
Uh, if you need anything,

37:21.917 --> 37:23.583
