38:01.000 --> 38:02.250
Hi.

38:02.250 --> 38:04.083
Hey.

38:04.083 --> 38:06.208
She's asleep.

38:06.208 --> 38:07.917
I'll be back in a minute.

38:07.917 --> 38:10.417
Okay.

38:10.417 --> 38:14.625
♪♪♪

